headline: Airbnb raised to Buy at Jefferies on durable growth
summary: Investing.com -- Jefferies upgraded Airbnb to Buy from Hold on Monday, citing durable growth in the company’s core lodging business and significant upside potential from experiences and take rate expansion.

headline: Airbnb Stock Could Rise Nearly 40%, Analyst Says. What’s Driving the Optimism.
summary: Airbnb  stock is a winner given the company’s durable growth and innovation plans, Jefferies argued on Monday.  Analysts led by John Colantuoni upgraded shares of the short-term rental company to Buy from Hold and increased their price target to $185 from $165.  Airbnb stock fell 1.7% to $132.08 in early trading.
